and Started\\\", \\\"message\\\": \\\"in progress: /bin/zsh -lc \\\\\\\"sed -n '1,260p' infra/compose/README.md\\\\\\\"\\\", \\\"raw_event\\\": {\\\"item\\\": {\\\"aggregated_output\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"/bin/zsh -lc \\\\\\\"sed -n '1,260p' infra/compose/README.md\\\\\\\"\\\", \\\"exit_code\\\": null, \\\"id\\\": \\\"item_38\\\", \\\"status\\\": \\\"in_progress\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"command_execution\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"item.started\\\"}, \\\"task_display_context\\\": {\\\"event_number\\\": 76, \\\"prompt_index\\\": 6, \\\"prompt_name\\\": \\\"05 \\\\u2014 Backend Settings, Env Loading, and `secrets.yaml` Support\\\", \\\"prompt_total\\\": 100}, \\\"timestap\\\": \\\"2026-03-31T21:44:14-07:00\\\"}\\n./prompts/05-backend-settings-and-secrets-loading.yolopilot.jsonlines:77:{\\\"color\\\": \\\"cyan\\\", \\\"emoji\\\": \\\"\\\\ud83d\\\\udee0\\\\ufe0f\\\", \\\"event_type\\\": \\\"Command Finished\\\", \\\"message\\\": \\\"completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \\\\\\\"sed -n '1,260p' infra/compose/README.md\\\\\\\"\\\", \\\"raw_event\\\": {\\\"item\\\": {\\\"aggregated_output\\\": \\\"# Compose\\\\n\\\\n`docker-compose.yml` in this directory is the canonical local stack definition for Storyteller.\\\\n\\\\nUse the repository wrapper script from the repo root:\\\\n\\\\n```bash\\\\n./scripts/dev-compose.sh up --build\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\nThat wrapper keeps the Compose file under `infra/` while preserving a simple developer entrypoint.\\\\n\\\\nCurrent local services:\\\\n\\\\n- `frontend` on `http://localhost:8566`\\\\n- `backend` on `http://localhost:8565`\\\\n- `postgres` on `localhost:8567`\\\\n- `gcs` on `http://localhost:8568`\\\\n- `browser` as the containerized QA runner\\\\n\\\", \\\"command\\\": \\\"/bin/zsh -lc \\\\\\\"sed -n '1,260p' infra/compose/README.md\\\\\\\"\\\", \\\"exit_code\\\": 0, \\\"id\\\": \\\"item_38\\\", \\\"status\\\": \\\"completed\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"command_execution\\\"}, \\\"type\\\": \\\"item.completed\\\"}, \\\"task_display_con